parameters.name: $src_coverage_items$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT
    prkr.policy_system_id,
    prkr.policy_cmm_container,
    prkr.policy_number,
    prkr.policy_module_number,
    prkr.policy_key,
    prkr.policy_key_code,
    prkr.risk_id,
    c.coverage_item_row_source_system_key AS coverage_item_id_from_source_system,
    c.class_code,
    c.coverage_item_code,
    c.source_system_coverage_item_type AS coverage_item_type_from_source_system,
    c.coverage_item_description,
    c.engine_displacement_in_cubic_centimeters,
    c.horsepower,
    c.inexperienced_operators,
    c.length,
    c.vehicle_model_name,
    c.vehicle_model_year,
    c.number_of_families,
    c.operating_area,
    c.pb_engine_hp1,
    c.pb_engine_model1,
    c.pb_max_speed,
    c.school_name,
    b.id as building_id,
    b.motorizedlandconveyanceind AS motorized_land_conveyance_description,
    b.typeofbusinessone as type_of_business_one,
    l.coverage_item_limit1,
    l.coverage_item_limit2,
    l.coverage_item_limit3,
    l.coverage_item_limit4,
    tgt.uw_dashboard_endorsement_detail_row_id,
    tgt.uw_dashboard_endorsement_detail_md5_hash_value 
FROM $$refined_schema.coverage_items c
LEFT JOIN $$dbo_schema.building_stg b
    ON c.source_system_system_id = b.systemid
   AND c.coverage_item_type = b.cmmcontainer
LEFT JOIN $$dbo_schema.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
    ON c.source_system_system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
   AND c.coverage_item_type = prkr.policy_cmm_container
   AND prkr.risk_id = b.parentid
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        systemid,
        parentid,
        cmmcontainer,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit1' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit1,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit2' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit2,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit3' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit3,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit4' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit4
    FROM $$dbo_schema.limit_stg
    GROUP BY systemid, parentid, cmmcontainer
) l
    ON c.source_system_system_id = l.systemid
   AND c.coverage_item_row_source_system_key = l.parentid
   AND c.coverage_item_type = l.cmmcontainer
left join $$dbo_schema.uw_dashboard_endorsement_details tgt 
on prkr.policy_system_id = tgt.policy_system_id 
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = tgt.policy_cmm_container 
and prkr.risk_id = tgt.risk_id 
and c.coverage_item_row_source_system_key = tgt.coverage_item_id_from_source_system 
and b.id = tgt.building_id 
and tgt.uw_dashboard_endorsement_detail_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
WHERE source_system_coverage_item_status = 'Active'
  AND prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
  AND c.coverage_item_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
  and c.coverage_item_row_effective_start_datetime >= $LastRunTime
  AND prkr.policy_cmm_container = 'Policy'
  AND c.coverage_item_type = 'Policy'
  AND l.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
  AND b.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT
    prkr.policy_system_id,
    prkr.policy_cmm_container,
    prkr.policy_number,
    prkr.policy_module_number,
    prkr.policy_key,
    prkr.policy_key_code,
    prkr.risk_id,
    c.coverage_item_row_source_system_key AS coverage_item_id_from_source_system,
    c.class_code,
    c.coverage_item_code,
    c.source_system_coverage_item_type AS coverage_item_type_from_source_system,
    c.coverage_item_description,
    c.engine_displacement_in_cubic_centimeters,
    c.horsepower,
    c.inexperienced_operators,
    c.length,
    c.vehicle_model_name,
    c.vehicle_model_year,
    c.number_of_families,
    c.operating_area,
    c.pb_engine_hp1,
    c.pb_engine_model1,
    c.pb_max_speed,
    c.school_name,
    b.building_application_id as building_id,
    b.building_application_motorized_land_conveyance_description AS motorized_land_conveyance_description,
    b.building_application_type_of_business_one        AS type_of_business_one,
    l.coverage_item_limit1,
    l.coverage_item_limit2,
    l.coverage_item_limit3,
    l.coverage_item_limit4,
    tgt.uw_dashboard_endorsement_detail_row_id,
    tgt.uw_dashboard_endorsement_detail_md5_hash_value 
FROM $$refined_schema.coverage_items c
LEFT JOIN $$dbo_schema.building_application_stg b
    ON c.source_system_system_id = b.building_application_system_id
   AND c.coverage_item_type = b.building_application_cmm_container 
LEFT JOIN $$dbo_schema.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
    ON c.source_system_system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
   AND c.coverage_item_type = prkr.policy_cmm_container
   AND prkr.risk_id = b.building_application_parent_id 
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        systemid,
        parentid,
        cmmcontainer,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit1' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit1,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit2' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit2,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit3' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit3,
        MAX(CASE WHEN limitcd = 'ItemLimit4' THEN value END) AS coverage_item_limit4
    FROM $$dbo_schema.limit_stg
    GROUP BY systemid, parentid, cmmcontainer
) l
    ON c.source_system_system_id = l.systemid
   AND c.coverage_item_row_source_system_key = l.parentid
   and c.coverage_item_type = l.cmmcontainer
left join $$dbo_schema.uw_dashboard_endorsement_details tgt 
on prkr.policy_system_id = tgt.policy_system_id 
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = tgt.policy_cmm_container 
and prkr.risk_id = tgt.risk_id 
and c.coverage_item_row_source_system_key = tgt.coverage_item_id_from_source_system 
and b.building_application_id = tgt.building_id 
and tgt.uw_dashboard_endorsement_detail_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
WHERE source_system_coverage_item_status = 'Active'
  AND prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
  AND c.coverage_item_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
  and c.coverage_item_row_effective_start_datetime >= $LastRunTime
  AND prkr.policy_cmm_container = 'Application'
  AND c.coverage_item_type = 'Application'
  AND l.cmmcontainer = 'Application'
  AND b.building_application_cmm_container = 'Application';
